column1: # Readings for 1910-1912 are for the Boltby Cliff Head No 1 site (SE494867) where the gauge resided before moving to the village.
# Readings for 1913-1917 are for the initial site in the village where the gauge resided before moving further to the south east.
# The reading for September 1926 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The reading for December 1938 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The reading for October 1949 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The reading for November 1950 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The readings for November and December 1953 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The reading for March 1956 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The station continued until 1977 according to MIDAS.
